      <title>Target认为今年的销售平坦，警告关税风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/target-sees-sales-flat-this-year-warns-of-tariff-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Target Corp.认为，可比的销售额在2025年的变化很小，低于平均分析师估计，而净销售额预计将攀升约1％。 Forrester副总裁兼首席分析师Sucharita Kodali检查了结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/target-sees-sales-flat-this-year-warns-of-tariff-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 12:37:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
