      <title>阿联酋的ADNOC目标是在Mega OMV交易之后的更多化学品增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/uae-s-adnoc-targets-more-chemicals-growth-after-mega-omv-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由ADNOC和OMV AG的化学单位合并成立的600亿美元公司的利润增长了50％以上，并且仍开放以进行进一步交易或建立新工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/uae-s-adnoc-targets-more-chemicals-growth-after-mega-omv-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 12:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
