    <item>
      <title>现在，美国产量曲线趋于增长风险，关税现在现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/us-yield-curve-steepens-on-growth-angst-with-tariffs-now-reality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的数周关税威胁得以实现，美国产量曲线在紧张的市场中变得陡峭，这引起了人们对对全球增长的影响的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/us-yield-curve-steepens-on-growth-angst-with-tariffs-now-reality</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
